            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.resumen.paragraph1Post': 'we support students through a stage where the decisions they make shape the course of their lives.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.resumen.paragraph2': 'Here, studying means thinking, creating, debating, and building your own life plan. Our model is based on constructionism: learning by doing, creating products and projects that extend beyond the classroom. We want students to arrive at university with judgment, skills, and emotional wellbeing — not just a diploma.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.vidaPre.mascotAlt': 'Alex recycling',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.vidaPre.title': 'College-prep life: leadership, social action, and experiences beyond the classroom',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.vidaPre.paragraph1': 'Life at Bilbao High School isn\'t limited to attending classes and taking exams. We promote social action projects, civic participation, and cultural activities.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.vidaPre.paragraph2': 'Students take part in debates, visits to institutions, and responsible leadership experiences. We want them to understand that their voice carries weight and can be used to build. High school is lived as a conscious rehearsal for adult life, with support and clear boundaries.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.vidaPre.imgAlt': 'Student explaining a project',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.idiomas.imgAlt': 'Students taking notes',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.idiomas.mascotAlt': 'Alex Basketball sticker',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.idiomas.title': 'Languages: advanced English and German as a third language',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.idiomas.paragraph1': 'At Bilbao High School, English is already taught at an advanced level, not as a starting point. We want students to be able to read, write, and present in English in university and professional settings.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.idiomas.paragraph2': 'We also add German as a third language at this stage. We chose it for the opportunities Germany offers Latin American talent today in study and work. Speaking English and German opens more doors to universities, scholarships, and professional projects in Mexico and abroad.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.dual.title': 'Dual certification with American Elite School',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.dual.paragraph1': 'At Bilbao High School we offer a dual certification program with American Elite School. Students complete online credits alongside their Mexican high school diploma.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.dual.paragraph2': 'Upon completion, they also earn a U.S. High School diploma, without depending on a single final exam. This diploma opens additional options in national and international university admissions. Dual certification doesn\'t replace the Mexican diploma — it complements and strengthens their academic profile.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.dual.imgAlt': 'Happy graduating students',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.vocacional.mascotAlt': 'Alex meditating',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.vocacional.title': 'Career guidance and life planning',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.vocacional.imgAlt': 'Students together',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.vocacional.paragraph1': 'Choosing a career shouldn\'t feel like a leap into the unknown. That\'s why career guidance is a key pillar at Bilbao High School. We conduct assessments, interviews, workshops, and university visits.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.vocacional.paragraph2': 'We also talk about family expectations, personal interests, and real fears. The goal isn\'t just choosing "what to study." It\'s also asking "who do I want to be" and "how do I want to contribute to the world."',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.title': 'Frequently asked questions about Bilbao High School',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.question1': 'What if my child still doesn\'t know what they want to study?',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.answer1': 'High school is precisely designed to support that search, not to demand immediate certainty. Career guidance helps clarify interests, skills, and real options step by step.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.question2': 'Why choose Bilbao High School over other private high schools?',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.answer2': 'Because here, high school is experienced as designing a future, not just a list of subjects. We integrate real projects, dual certification, languages, and close support into every decision.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.question3': 'Is dual certification with American Elite School included in tuition?',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.answer3': 'No. Dual certification is paid separately, at a very low cost compared to similar programs. It\'s an accessible option that strengthens their academic profile and opens more university doors.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.question4': 'What if my child arrives with a different English level than the group?',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.answer4': 'We offer differentiated English levels in high school. We support each student in progressively advancing to the next level.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.question5': 'Can students from other high schools, systems, or countries enroll?',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.faq.answer5': 'Yes, we welcome students from other educational systems and even other countries. That diversity enriches campus life and creates a community with wonderfully rich culture.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.cta.mascotAlt': 'Somos Bilbao',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.cta.title': 'Come meet us',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.cta.paragraph': 'If you want your children\'s high school years to be a space for designing their future, not just completing credits, come see it up close.',
            'niveles-academicos-preparatoria.cta.button': 'Schedule a visit to Bilbao High School',

