            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.intro.body1DropCap': 'I',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.intro.body1Pre': 'n the Colegio Bilbao, the educational model has a name of its own: ',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.intro.body1Post': '. It stands for Vincula, Indaga, Descubre and Aporta — Connect, Inquire, Discover and Contribute. From preschool through high school, this model guides decisions, classes and projects.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.intro.body2': 'It\'s our framework for learning that has meaning and direction. It helps every family understand what we\'re aiming for and why. It also shows real progress, beyond a grade.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.vincula.imgAlt': 'Connect',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.vincula.title': 'Connect',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.vincula.desc': 'Learning with others, through relationships that care. It\'s lived through community, a culture of peace and close accompaniment.',
