            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.indaga.title': 'Inquire',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.indaga.desc': 'Asking with intention and respect. It\'s lived through critical thinking, guided dialogue and curiosity that never fades.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.descubre.imgAlt': 'Discover',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.descubre.title': 'Discover',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.descubre.desc': 'Learning by doing and connecting with the real world. It\'s lived through projects and experiences that become memories.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.aporta.imgAlt': 'Contribute',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.aporta.title': 'Contribute',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.grid.aporta.desc': 'Turning what\'s learned into meaningful action. Students develop an ethical compass to make an impact, not just pass a test.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.habit.watermark': 'FUTURE',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.habit.quotePre': 'When VIDA becomes a habit, ',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.habit.quoteEm': 'the future changes.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.habit.subtitle': 'In Mexico City, choosing a school means choosing a way of living childhood.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.title': 'Frequently asked questions',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.q1.question': 'Is VIDA an educational model or just marketing?',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.q1.answer': 'VIDA is a real educational model that guides classroom decisions. It also works as a clear language for families to understand our methodology.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.q2.question': 'How does it affect academic performance?',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.q2.answer': 'It aims for deep understanding and applicable skills, which usually translates into better performance, greater autonomy and lasting learning.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.q3.question': 'Does it apply the same way at every level?',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.q3.answer': 'Yes, it\'s the common thread. The form changes with age, but the spirit of Vincula, Indaga, Descubre and Aporta stays the same.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.q4.question': 'What role does the family play?',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.q4.answer': 'The family is a key ally. We seek consistency between home and school through clear communication, without overriding the student\'s autonomy.',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.q5.question': 'How can I see that it\'s really lived out?',
            'modelo-educativo-modelo-vida.faq.q5.answer': 'The clearest way is to visit and watch a class in action. That\'s where you can see the connection, the inquiry and the contribution happening in real time.',
