            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.hero.supertitle': 'Integral Learning',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.hero.title': 'Five paths to learning with purpose',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.hero.subtitle': 'Science, humanities, arts, technology and active living. At Colegio Bilbao, learning isn\'t confined to subjects — it\'s lived as real experiences.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.hero.imgAlt': 'Integral Learning',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.hero.floatLabelPre': 'Paths of the',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.intro.highlight': 'At Colegio Bilbao, learning isn\'t confined to separate subjects. It\'s lived as experiences that build judgment, curiosity and real skills.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.intro.body': 'That\'s why we educate from preschool through high school with an integral, human outlook. What\'s worked on at school shows up at home and takes root in community.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.ciencia.imgAlt': 'Science',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.ciencia.mascotAlt': 'Alex the Scientist',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.ciencia.title': 'How we live science',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.ciencia.text1': 'At Bilbao, science is born from curiosity and becomes method. From an early age, students observe, ask questions and test ideas with guidance. They learn through experimentation, recording and reflection.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.ciencia.text2': 'The campus and its open spaces also become a living laboratory. This strengthens critical thinking and the confidence to solve real problems.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.humanidades.imgAlt': 'Humanities',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.humanidades.mascotAlt': 'Alex the Reader',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.humanidades.title': 'How we work with the humanities',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.humanidades.text': 'The humanities teach students to think, engage in dialogue and understand human contexts. We foster reading, oral expression and purposeful writing.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.humanidades.item1': 'Debate and argumentation teams.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.humanidades.item2': 'Educational visits (Senate, Chamber of Deputies).',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.humanidades.item3': 'Understanding that your voice matters and carries responsibility.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.artes.imgAlt': 'Arts',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.artes.mascotAlt': 'Alex the Artist',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.artes.title': 'The arts as a language',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.artes.text1': 'At Bilbao, art isn\'t decoration — it\'s deep formation. It\'s lived as a tool to create, collaborate and build tolerance for frustration.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.artes.text2': 'Artistic practice develops discipline, sensitivity and a critical eye. It also opens a safe space for self-expression and being seen by peers.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.tecnologia.imgAlt': 'Technology',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.tecnologia.mascotAlt': 'Alex the Techie',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.tecnologia.title': 'Technology in service of learning',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.tecnologia.text1': 'We use technology to enhance learning, not to replace what\'s human. It\'s integrated as a tool for research, creation and presenting projects.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.tecnologia.text2': 'We aim for logical thinking, digital judgment and responsible use. The goal is for students to build, not just consume, preparing them for the future with autonomy.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.deportes.imgAlt': 'Sports',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.deportes.mascotAlt': 'Alex Playing Volleyball',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.deportes.title': 'Sports and active living',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.deportes.text1': 'Sports shape the body, character and community. We encourage habits of movement, discipline and teamwork.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.pillar.deportes.text2': 'Active living is understood as wellbeing, fellowship and consistency. Students learn to take care of themselves and to belong to a group.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.faq.title': 'Frequently asked questions',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.faq.q1.question': 'How do you keep academics from feeling disconnected?',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.faq.q1.answer': 'We work with experiences and projects that cross different disciplines around a shared purpose. That helps students understand better and remember longer.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.faq.q2.question': 'How do you support students with different strengths?',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.faq.q2.answer': 'We observe each student\'s learning style and adjust strategies with close follow-up. The goal is real progress, not unfair comparisons.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.faq.q3.question': 'How important is debate and public speaking?',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.faq.q3.answer': 'It\'s essential for critical thinking, leadership and university life. It\'s practiced with structure and respect, not confrontation.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.faq.q4.question': 'Does technology mean more screen time?',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.faq.q4.answer': 'We aim for meaningful creation and digital judgment, not just screen time. Technology is used as a means, not an end.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.cta.mascotAlt': 'Alex Mascot',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.cta.title': 'Live it up close',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.cta.desc': 'If you want to see how these experiences change the way students learn, the best way is to experience it up close.',
            'modelo-educativo-aprendizaje-integral.cta.button': 'Book a visit',

