            'terminos-y-condiciones.seccion11.titulo': '11) Site availability and security',
            'terminos-y-condiciones.seccion11.parrafo1': 'Colegio Bilbao strives to keep the Site available and secure, but does not guarantee uninterrupted, error-free operation free from interruptions due to technical causes, maintenance, third-party failures, force majeure, or events beyond its reasonable control.',
            'terminos-y-condiciones.seccion11.parrafo2': 'Users are responsible for maintaining basic security measures (for example, antivirus software, an updated browser) to reduce risk while browsing the internet.',
